{
  "stem": "11296.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And two days later-- yeah-- in the same evening-- the same evening, I saw a lot of soldiers-- Polish-- with artillery, with old, you know, everything was on horses, the soldiers on horses with wagons going to the front.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had to go through mine town to go to the front.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, you know, and-- and people start, you know, people was very afraid what's going to happen.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So everybody-- so the next day, whole families start running.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They run to Warsaw-- I, my sisters, between them, my two sisters took the children.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my father was there, my sister, my other sister, who was not married, she was-- she was working.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One, it was-- my oldest was Frida.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my-- mine second one was Esther.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my third, who is alive, is Hannah-- Hanka-- Hannah.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my brother was Abe.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So my brother and me, we stayed with our mother.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the other-- the other family, all of them went to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was unbelievable what was going on at the roads.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "People didn't have transportation.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Everybody was walking-- walking because they said they're not going to bomb Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They're going to, you know-- they're going to-- they're not-- the soldiers, they have a big fortress there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they're going to fight, and not going  to let him in.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "This-- this whole episode took four weeks-- took them four weeks till the-- the soldiers, you know, the Germans took over Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And there was-- this, I can't-- I-- I was not there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So I cannot tell.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The only thing I know, Warsaw was bombed terrible.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Because when they came back-- they came back, you know, after four or five weeks.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I remember between there was the high holy days.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
